WEBVTT

00:00:00.172 --> 00:00:01.727
Five million as compensation?

00:00:01.727 --> 00:00:03.336
[Episode 5]
[Shielding you from the world's evil]

00:00:03.336 --> 00:00:06.105
That amount is completely unreasonable.

00:00:06.940 --> 00:00:09.042
May I ask...

00:00:09.042 --> 00:00:12.678
Mr. He, what do you do for a living?

00:00:13.580 --> 00:00:15.714
I run an inn.

00:00:16.349 --> 00:00:18.451
An inn owner... I don't blame you, Mr. He.

00:00:18.451 --> 00:00:19.586
-

00:00:19.586 --> 00:00:21.021
You might not be familiar with
how things work in our industry.

00:00:21.021 --> 00:00:23.723
-

00:00:23.723 --> 00:00:26.192
Actually, this five million...

00:00:26.192 --> 00:00:29.496
Our company has contracts with artists.

00:00:29.496 --> 00:00:31.765
There are also supply chain contracts,

00:00:31.765 --> 00:00:33.466
plus the cost of the discarded prints.

00:00:33.466 --> 00:00:37.604
Adding it all up, five million is actually...

00:00:37.604 --> 00:00:40.440
I've begged everyone I could

00:00:40.440 --> 00:00:42.908
to get the amount down this low.

00:00:44.844 --> 00:00:46.212
How about this?

00:00:46.212 --> 00:00:48.748
Bring out the contracts one by one.

00:00:48.748 --> 00:00:50.308
We'll go through them together
to see if it really adds up to that much.

00:00:50.308 --> 00:00:53.586
-

00:00:53.586 --> 00:00:54.954
I don't have the contracts on hand,
but I think there's something more important.

00:00:54.954 --> 00:00:57.424
-

00:00:57.424 --> 00:00:58.991
Hang on...

00:01:02.062 --> 00:01:04.964
Please take a look at this affidavit.

00:01:04.964 --> 00:01:07.092
Xiang Yong signed this.

00:01:07.092 --> 00:01:10.414
I've confirmed it with him many times.
[Voluntary Resignation]

00:01:10.414 --> 00:01:13.106
[He Xiang Yong]

00:01:13.840 --> 00:01:14.974
Such a huge amount,
and you're making Xiang Yong pay alone?

00:01:14.974 --> 00:01:17.277
-

00:01:17.277 --> 00:01:18.411
Mr. President...

00:01:18.411 --> 00:01:21.046
Sorry, I'm just a publisher.

00:01:23.249 --> 00:01:25.017
Sir.

00:01:25.618 --> 00:01:27.187
Are you taking advantage of his youth
to make him a scapegoat?

00:01:27.187 --> 00:01:29.521
-

00:01:35.228 --> 00:01:39.531
Mr. He, it really hurts to hear you say that.

00:01:40.867 --> 00:01:43.169
To be honest, since I started this business,

00:01:43.169 --> 00:01:47.140
what I've valued most
is being fair, just, and transparent.

00:01:47.140 --> 00:01:48.808
We might not be a large corporation,

00:01:48.808 --> 00:01:51.944
but we're a publishing house with a conscience.

00:01:53.147 --> 00:01:54.147
It's fine.

00:01:54.147 --> 00:01:56.950
Mr. He, it's okay if you don't trust me.

00:01:56.950 --> 00:01:58.017
I'll have Xiang Yong's former colleague
to come and explain things to you.

00:01:58.017 --> 00:01:59.919
-

00:01:59.919 --> 00:02:01.120
How about that?

00:02:02.019 --> 00:02:04.424
This is He Xiang Yong's father.

00:02:04.424 --> 00:02:07.060
He thinks we've misunderstood Xiang Yong.

00:02:07.060 --> 00:02:09.229
Xiang Yong did cause a huge mess.

00:02:09.229 --> 00:02:11.431
He's turned the whole company upside down.

00:02:11.431 --> 00:02:13.933
- Exactly.
- We've been cleaning up his mess.

00:02:13.933 --> 00:02:17.203
Mr. He, from the time he was an intern,

00:02:17.203 --> 00:02:19.139
he's made so many mistakes.

00:02:19.139 --> 00:02:20.240
He's screwed up so many times.

00:02:20.240 --> 00:02:22.475
We're constantly cleaning up after him.

00:02:22.475 --> 00:02:23.943
All right, that's enough.

00:02:23.943 --> 00:02:25.411
Hey, show some respect.

00:02:25.411 --> 00:02:28.314
His father is right there.

00:02:32.699 --> 00:02:35.734
If it's really Xiang Yong's fault,

00:02:38.791 --> 00:02:40.660
then I thank you all

00:02:40.660 --> 00:02:43.396
for taking care of him all these years.

00:02:43.396 --> 00:02:46.599
If your consciences are truly clear,

00:02:46.599 --> 00:02:48.535
then I wish your company great success and soaring profits.

00:02:48.535 --> 00:02:50.236
-

00:02:50.236 --> 00:02:52.171
May you never choke while eating,
never trip while walking,

00:02:52.171 --> 00:02:54.740
and may you never encounter
another He Xiang Yong.

00:02:58.511 --> 00:03:00.713
Mr. He, those are such kind words.

00:03:00.713 --> 00:03:01.948
I'm truly touched, really.

00:03:01.948 --> 00:03:03.249
For those of us in business,

00:03:03.249 --> 00:03:04.384
what we fear most is an employee like Xiang Yong.

00:03:04.384 --> 00:03:07.186
-

00:03:08.087 --> 00:03:09.357
By the way,

00:03:09.357 --> 00:03:12.058
Xiang Yong's friend called saying they would handle this matter.

00:03:12.058 --> 00:03:15.595
But actually, we haven't heard anything back.

00:03:15.595 --> 00:03:16.663
I should remind you, Mr. He.

00:03:16.663 --> 00:03:17.663
If this continues,
we might have to proceed with legal action.

00:03:17.663 --> 00:03:21.537
-

00:03:26.906 --> 00:03:30.009
Don't you threaten me with the law.

00:03:32.378 --> 00:03:35.247
Xiang Yong said he'd take responsibility.

00:03:36.049 --> 00:03:38.784
So, we'll see it through to the end.

00:03:39.819 --> 00:03:40.987
Then I'll leave it to you.
Someone see Mr. He out.

00:03:40.987 --> 00:03:43.255
-

00:04:36.709 --> 00:04:38.711
What an unscrupulous company.

00:04:38.711 --> 00:04:41.714
This is pure workplace bullying.

00:04:41.714 --> 00:04:44.317
That brat of mine...

00:04:44.317 --> 00:04:46.953
He came back to the island,

00:04:46.953 --> 00:04:49.989
but he wouldn't tell me anything.

00:04:49.989 --> 00:04:52.158
I'm not surprised. Like father, like son.

00:04:52.158 --> 00:04:54.494
Xiang Yong is just like you.

00:04:54.494 --> 00:04:57.230
He won't let you see his pain,

00:04:57.230 --> 00:04:59.265
just like you won't let him know
about your kidney problems.

00:04:59.265 --> 00:05:01.100
You're the one with an enlarged prostate!
Who has problems?

00:05:01.100 --> 00:05:03.336
Keep it down.

00:05:03.336 --> 00:05:04.767
My health is a minor issue.

00:05:04.767 --> 00:05:07.305
There's nothing to talk about.

00:05:07.305 --> 00:05:09.275
Yeah, right.

00:05:09.275 --> 00:05:10.476
Every time Xiang Yong comes home,
you just sit there drinking.

00:05:10.476 --> 00:05:12.245
-

00:05:12.245 --> 00:05:15.181
And then? You prepare the freshest seafood.

00:05:15.181 --> 00:05:17.884
Anyone can see
how happy you are that he's back.

00:05:17.884 --> 00:05:19.718
You call that a minor issue?

00:05:23.790 --> 00:05:25.625
So, what now?

00:05:25.625 --> 00:05:28.227
Selling the house is the only way?

00:05:30.930 --> 00:05:33.966
I tried to get a bank loan,

00:05:33.966 --> 00:05:36.802
but the house is too old to be worth much.

00:05:37.670 --> 00:05:39.305
I'm getting old, too.

00:05:39.305 --> 00:05:41.674
I don't want a situation where...

00:05:41.674 --> 00:05:45.711
after I'm gone,
Xiang Yong is stuck with my debts.

00:05:47.347 --> 00:05:48.381
Luckily...

00:05:48.381 --> 00:05:49.415
Luckily, that David guy...
offered just enough.

00:05:49.415 --> 00:05:52.719
-

00:05:52.719 --> 00:05:54.187
Sell it.

00:05:54.187 --> 00:05:56.688
Of course, sell it. Sell it quickly.

00:05:58.224 --> 00:06:01.360
You mean David, the influencer?

00:06:03.062 --> 00:06:04.530
He's very sincere.

00:06:04.530 --> 00:06:06.065
He's not even from our island.

00:06:06.065 --> 00:06:07.533
When he heard I was selling,

00:06:07.533 --> 00:06:09.635
he said he'd take a boat to see it right away.

00:06:09.635 --> 00:06:12.070
I'm grateful to him.

00:06:23.716 --> 00:06:26.352
Why are you cutting so much?

00:06:26.352 --> 00:06:27.887
Don't sneak a bite.

00:06:27.887 --> 00:06:30.289
That's for our guest.

00:06:35.828 --> 00:06:37.497
Look, he's here.

00:06:37.497 --> 00:06:38.831
Hurry up and get it ready.

00:06:38.831 --> 00:06:40.967
Stop cutting already.

00:06:40.967 --> 00:06:43.669
Snakestyle toss!

00:06:45.004 --> 00:06:47.139
Mr. He!

00:06:47.940 --> 00:06:49.509
Watch out!

00:06:49.509 --> 00:06:52.110
Careful!

00:06:52.979 --> 00:06:55.181
Nice catch.

00:06:55.181 --> 00:06:57.784
A gift for our first meeting.

00:06:57.784 --> 00:07:00.386
This is a crystal from my new collection.

00:07:00.386 --> 00:07:02.388
- A crystal?
- It looks pretty good, yeah?

00:07:02.388 --> 00:07:03.756
Wow, impressive.

00:07:03.756 --> 00:07:05.958
This is my good friend, Hua.

00:07:05.958 --> 00:07:09.195
Hello, Hua.

00:07:09.195 --> 00:07:10.430
Have a seat.

00:07:10.430 --> 00:07:11.931
It's so hot.

00:07:11.931 --> 00:07:14.000
This weather is a specialty of Starry Islet.

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:16.335
It's like a fairy tale world, you know?

00:07:16.335 --> 00:07:17.336
It's actually quite comfortable.

00:07:17.336 --> 00:07:19.039
What would you like to drink?

00:07:19.039 --> 00:07:20.973
Man Niu.

00:07:20.973 --> 00:07:23.810
Xiao You, get a bottle of Man Niu.

00:07:23.810 --> 00:07:24.911
Take some photos.
These are all old houses.

00:07:24.911 --> 00:07:26.179
-

00:07:26.179 --> 00:07:27.413
You don't see them much anymore.

00:07:27.413 --> 00:07:29.615
He's my employee.

00:07:29.615 --> 00:07:31.117
Take a photo of that dilapidated building, too.

00:07:31.117 --> 00:07:32.952
See what we can renovate.

00:07:32.952 --> 00:07:35.221
Keep filming.

00:07:35.221 --> 00:07:37.956
Just take photos of everything.

00:07:45.698 --> 00:07:47.833
What are you doing?

00:07:52.705 --> 00:07:54.774
This is my bread and butter.

00:07:54.774 --> 00:07:56.476
If I can't even do this well,

00:07:56.476 --> 00:07:59.912
how would I have the money
to buy a inn from you?

00:07:59.912 --> 00:08:00.813
You're too modest.

00:08:00.813 --> 00:08:02.714
David,

00:08:03.416 --> 00:08:04.751
it's an honor to meet you.

00:08:04.751 --> 00:08:05.883
I've watched your videos.
I'm a subscriber.

00:08:05.883 --> 00:08:07.353
-

00:08:07.353 --> 00:08:08.621
His content is so diverse.

00:08:08.621 --> 00:08:11.390
And his view counts are through the roof.

00:08:11.390 --> 00:08:13.826
Vlogs, diving, food reviews...

00:08:13.826 --> 00:08:16.361
They're all so dumb.

00:08:17.630 --> 00:08:18.964
What?

00:08:19.866 --> 00:08:23.101
I meant "dope." They're very dope.

00:08:24.604 --> 00:08:27.006
But I heard that nowadays,

00:08:27.006 --> 00:08:30.610
views and traffic can be bought.

00:08:30.610 --> 00:08:31.777
I wouldn't know, though.

00:08:31.777 --> 00:08:33.212
Yeah, I wanted to ask you about that.

00:08:33.212 --> 00:08:35.281
Since I don't run a channel myself.

00:08:35.281 --> 00:08:37.350
I've heard rumors about that, too.

00:08:37.350 --> 00:08:39.886
But I have no idea how to buy those things.

00:08:39.886 --> 00:08:42.021
After all, I rely on my own merits.

00:08:42.021 --> 00:08:44.156
- I don't know where to find those channels.
- Right.

00:08:44.156 --> 00:08:45.825
Just like how I want to buy this inn now,

00:08:45.825 --> 00:08:48.661
I'd also like to ask you for advice

00:08:48.661 --> 00:08:50.962
on how to run a inn.

00:08:51.731 --> 00:08:54.400
Sir, about the paperwork...

00:08:54.400 --> 00:08:58.304
Will you handle the legal agent, or should I?

00:08:58.304 --> 00:09:00.907
You have more experience buying property.

00:09:00.907 --> 00:09:01.907
- You handle everything.
- Sure.

00:09:01.907 --> 00:09:03.576
-

00:09:03.576 --> 00:09:05.411
I'll take care of it then.

00:09:05.411 --> 00:09:07.413
Excuse me, I'd like to ask,

00:09:07.413 --> 00:09:09.749
since your channel is so successful,

00:09:09.749 --> 00:09:12.752
why do you want to invest in real estate?

00:09:12.752 --> 00:09:14.921
Investment... always comes with risks.

00:09:14.921 --> 00:09:17.590
And not every job can be a side hustle.

00:09:17.590 --> 00:09:19.358
My dad always tells me,

00:09:19.358 --> 00:09:21.127
if a person is too greedy,

00:09:21.127 --> 00:09:23.568
it usually doesn't end well.

00:09:25.498 --> 00:09:26.563
That's not the case for me.

00:09:26.563 --> 00:09:28.234
Because with my other jobs,

00:09:28.234 --> 00:09:30.770
I can make money while lying down.

00:09:30.770 --> 00:09:32.071
So, I thought, by running a inn,

00:09:32.071 --> 00:09:32.739
-

00:09:32.739 --> 00:09:36.208
I could dive in and experience local life for myself.

00:09:36.208 --> 00:09:38.143
Where's my Man Niu?

00:09:39.111 --> 00:09:41.581
- Where's the Man Niu?
- Hao Wei, that Man Niu...

00:09:41.581 --> 00:09:43.115
We're out of Man Niu.

00:09:43.115 --> 00:09:44.183
Is a yogurt drink okay?

00:09:44.183 --> 00:09:46.419
Forget it, never mind.

00:09:46.419 --> 00:09:48.721
Sir, I've been thinking...

00:09:48.721 --> 00:09:52.591
I want to tear down the whole building.

00:09:55.761 --> 00:09:58.264
I think it's a bit too old,
and it's not that safe.

00:09:58.264 --> 00:10:00.333
-

00:10:00.333 --> 00:10:02.201
So, I'm thinking of changing it to...

00:10:02.201 --> 00:10:04.203
Greek style, Turkish style, or Spanish style. Anything works.

00:10:04.203 --> 00:10:05.838
-

00:10:05.838 --> 00:10:07.540
Or if you have...

00:10:07.540 --> 00:10:08.774
Or if there's something you want,
you can always tell me.

00:10:08.774 --> 00:10:09.842
-

00:10:09.842 --> 00:10:13.813
David, I think you really don't get it.

00:10:13.813 --> 00:10:15.915
Do you know this is a historical site?

00:10:15.915 --> 00:10:17.917
Do you know how much history it has?

00:10:17.917 --> 00:10:19.418
Do you know how many people come here

00:10:19.418 --> 00:10:20.853
just because the inn looks like this?

00:10:20.853 --> 00:10:22.922
I think you're really clueless.

00:10:22.922 --> 00:10:24.790
Maybe you shouldn't invest in real estate.

00:10:24.790 --> 00:10:26.492
You should just go back
to filming your tacky vlogs.

00:10:26.492 --> 00:10:28.527
Zhong Xiao You.

00:10:30.296 --> 00:10:32.697
Please don't be rude to my guest.

00:10:33.432 --> 00:10:35.768
Let's talk about this later.

00:10:35.768 --> 00:10:38.136
Do you really have to sell the inn?

00:10:39.305 --> 00:10:41.706
Is there really no other way?

00:10:52.852 --> 00:10:56.127
It's my house, and I'll decide.

00:10:58.958 --> 00:11:00.826
I'm so sorry.

00:11:01.661 --> 00:11:02.662
It's fine, sir.

00:11:02.662 --> 00:11:04.997
Maybe you should discuss it
among yourselves first?

00:11:04.997 --> 00:11:06.932
No, there's no need for that.

00:11:06.932 --> 00:11:08.634
- We're selling. We're definitely selling.
- Okay.

00:11:08.634 --> 00:11:11.671
You now, there's a terrace on the second floor.

00:11:11.671 --> 00:11:13.039
It has an unbeatable sea view. Let me show you.

00:11:13.039 --> 00:11:14.507
- Sure.
- Let's go.

00:11:14.507 --> 00:11:16.374
This way, please.

00:11:17.109 --> 00:11:18.177
Zhong Xiao You.

00:11:18.177 --> 00:11:19.811
That's your name, yeah?

00:11:20.513 --> 00:11:22.648
Are you just afraid of losing your job?

00:11:22.648 --> 00:11:24.617
Don't you worry.

00:11:24.617 --> 00:11:26.686
Once I buy this inn,

00:11:26.686 --> 00:11:29.689
you can all come and work for me.

00:11:29.689 --> 00:11:30.823
No, that's not it at all.

00:11:30.823 --> 00:11:32.091
This way, please.

00:11:32.091 --> 00:11:33.626
Let's go.

00:11:33.626 --> 00:11:35.961
- Turn left up ahead.
- Keep an eye on him.

00:11:35.961 --> 00:11:37.163
After you turn right,

00:11:37.163 --> 00:11:40.699
the view connects right to the sea.

00:11:41.767 --> 00:11:43.803
Hao Wei, Xiao You.

00:11:43.803 --> 00:11:46.539
Show them around.

00:11:46.539 --> 00:11:48.240
Okay.

00:11:48.240 --> 00:11:49.575
What are you doing?

00:11:49.575 --> 00:11:50.843
You're acting very strange today.

00:11:50.843 --> 00:11:52.366
Xiao You.

00:11:56.849 --> 00:11:58.417
Well...

00:11:58.417 --> 00:12:01.420
Let's go to the front desk. Come on, follow me.

00:12:01.420 --> 00:12:03.255
This way.

00:12:03.255 --> 00:12:05.596
This is our reception desk.

00:12:32.952 --> 00:12:34.353
Are you serious?

00:12:34.353 --> 00:12:36.621
He really bought it from Yilan.

00:12:39.490 --> 00:12:43.295
Hama-chan was right.

00:12:43.295 --> 00:12:44.864
He said if you're suspicious,
just check his Instagram stories.

00:12:44.864 --> 00:12:47.299
-

00:13:10.489 --> 00:13:12.224
Seeing you eat so happily,
I guess you two have made up?

00:13:12.224 --> 00:13:15.094
-

00:13:15.094 --> 00:13:16.829
Your son has a big heart.

00:13:16.829 --> 00:13:19.598
Friends don't hold grudges.

00:13:19.598 --> 00:13:21.667
Are you guys really just friends?

00:13:21.667 --> 00:13:23.836
Don't you like Hama-chan?

00:13:23.836 --> 00:13:26.338
I don't like him. Don't talk nonsense.

00:13:27.907 --> 00:13:31.110
Liking someone is nothing to be ashamed of.

00:13:31.110 --> 00:13:32.111
Hear me out.

00:13:32.111 --> 00:13:35.181
If you love someone, say it out loud, okay?

00:13:35.181 --> 00:13:37.248
I don't like him.

00:13:38.484 --> 00:13:39.819
It's Hua's birthday tomorrow.

00:13:39.819 --> 00:13:41.320
You must invite Hama-chan.

00:13:41.320 --> 00:13:43.188
We'll see.

00:13:44.023 --> 00:13:45.257
Li Wan Zhe, get on the bike.

00:13:45.257 --> 00:13:47.126
- Do you want to eat first?
- Hurry up.

00:13:47.126 --> 00:13:48.561
What?

00:13:48.561 --> 00:13:50.629
Why are you in such a rush?

00:13:50.629 --> 00:13:53.432
Mom, I'm going out for a bit.

00:13:53.432 --> 00:13:55.467
Are you taking me out to have fun?

00:13:56.202 --> 00:13:58.336
Why are you riding so fast today?

00:14:01.407 --> 00:14:03.943
- Come with me.
- Wait, I haven't taken off my helmet yet.

00:14:03.943 --> 00:14:07.178
- Hurry up.
- What are you doing? What's the rush?

00:14:07.780 --> 00:14:10.282
Why the rush?

00:14:10.282 --> 00:14:11.350
Are you running an errand for a guest?

00:14:11.350 --> 00:14:13.018
Do you have your ID with you?

00:14:13.018 --> 00:14:15.087
I think so.

00:14:15.087 --> 00:14:16.822
Quick! Buy me a ticket back to the main island!

00:14:16.822 --> 00:14:18.257
- Hurry up.
- Why are you going back to the main island?

00:14:18.257 --> 00:14:19.625
Just go buy it first.

00:14:19.625 --> 00:14:20.960
If you don't tell me, I won't buy it.

00:14:20.960 --> 00:14:23.194
My house is being sold!

00:14:28.400 --> 00:14:31.203
So, that's how you got into debt.

00:14:31.203 --> 00:14:33.205
This is so infuriating.

00:14:33.205 --> 00:14:34.440
When I called your boss back then,
I should've cursed him out.

00:14:34.440 --> 00:14:36.871
-

00:14:42.948 --> 00:14:45.696
How did it come to this?

00:14:47.519 --> 00:14:49.488
It's all because of that stupid shooting star.

00:14:49.488 --> 00:14:52.223
Now I can't do anything.

00:14:54.693 --> 00:14:56.762
You can't blame the shooting star.

00:14:56.762 --> 00:14:59.531
Anyway, what's done is done.

00:14:59.531 --> 00:15:01.267
Yeah.

00:15:01.267 --> 00:15:03.602
Since it's already happened, I have to face it.

00:15:03.602 --> 00:15:04.770
I'll pay my own debts.

00:15:04.770 --> 00:15:06.672
No one can touch my home.

00:15:06.672 --> 00:15:08.374
Are you going to help me buy a ticket or not?

00:15:08.374 --> 00:15:09.508
What's the point of buying a ticket?

00:15:09.508 --> 00:15:11.076
What can you do back on the main island?

00:15:11.076 --> 00:15:13.112
I don't care.

00:15:13.112 --> 00:15:14.179
My dad is selling the house because of me.

00:15:14.179 --> 00:15:16.982
I can't just sit here and do nothing.

00:15:16.982 --> 00:15:19.071
I'm going back to talk to my boss.

00:15:21.020 --> 00:15:22.388
Fine, you want to go back?

00:15:22.388 --> 00:15:24.256
Do you have money? Do you have an ID?

00:15:24.256 --> 00:15:26.692
That's why I need you to buy it for me.

00:15:26.692 --> 00:15:28.360
Fine, I'll buy it. Then what?

00:15:28.360 --> 00:15:30.229
How are you going to get the five million?

00:15:30.229 --> 00:15:32.264
Even if you went to loan sharks now,
no one would lend you a cent.

00:15:32.264 --> 00:15:33.299
Don't you realize that?

00:15:33.299 --> 00:15:36.034
And in what capacity will you face your boss?

00:15:54.386 --> 00:15:55.912
Mr. He...

00:15:57.156 --> 00:15:59.558
Since you're so reluctant to let it go,

00:15:59.558 --> 00:16:01.893
why do you have to sell the inn?

00:16:07.599 --> 00:16:09.567
Well...

00:16:10.648 --> 00:16:13.479
Sometimes we have no choice in life.

00:16:43.335 --> 00:16:45.270
I'm sorry.

00:16:50.147 --> 00:16:51.977
Hao Wei.

00:16:51.977 --> 00:16:54.179
Go help me take stock of the driftwood.

00:16:54.179 --> 00:16:55.840
Okay.

00:18:32.611 --> 00:18:34.580
Chief, we can handle things here.

00:18:34.580 --> 00:18:35.948
I already finished this part downstairs.

00:18:35.948 --> 00:18:36.982
Okay.

00:18:36.982 --> 00:18:38.584
How is it? How's the fire coming along?

00:18:38.584 --> 00:18:40.219
It's going. It's fine.

00:18:40.219 --> 00:18:42.084
You're fanning it so slowly.

00:18:42.084 --> 00:18:43.122
Let me do it.

00:18:43.122 --> 00:18:44.122
Yue, go check on the ice.

00:18:44.122 --> 00:18:45.390
Being the village chief is hard work.

00:18:45.390 --> 00:18:47.159
- I have to do everything myself.
- I'm worried there's not enough booze.

00:18:47.159 --> 00:18:49.928
If you're no longer the chief...

00:18:49.928 --> 00:18:52.064
Happy birthday to you.

00:18:52.064 --> 00:18:55.267
Happy birthday to you.

00:18:55.267 --> 00:18:58.203
Happy birthday to you.

00:18:58.203 --> 00:19:00.072
Thank you.

00:19:00.072 --> 00:19:01.507
Wait a minute.

00:19:01.507 --> 00:19:02.540
You have to make a wish first.
It's a Starry Islet tradition.

00:19:02.540 --> 00:19:03.974
-

00:19:03.974 --> 00:19:06.144
- Make a wish.
- Make a wish.

00:19:07.312 --> 00:19:09.147
Okay, let's do this.

00:19:10.249 --> 00:19:11.716
Okay.

00:19:12.451 --> 00:19:14.285
All right, all right.

00:19:15.220 --> 00:19:17.689
- Cheers.
- Come on, cheers.

00:19:17.689 --> 00:19:19.391
To the most handsome man on Starry Islet, Hua!

00:19:19.391 --> 00:19:20.692
Good.

00:19:20.692 --> 00:19:22.027
I wish you all good health.

00:19:22.027 --> 00:19:23.761
And may all your wishes come true.

00:19:27.833 --> 00:19:30.235
You youngsters, get moving!

00:19:30.235 --> 00:19:32.003
Tell me what you want to eat.

00:19:34.873 --> 00:19:36.441
- What do you want?
- Green peppers.

00:19:36.441 --> 00:19:38.542
Okay. What else?

00:19:40.078 --> 00:19:41.113
- Mushrooms.
- Mushrooms?

00:19:41.113 --> 00:19:42.513
Yes.

00:19:44.216 --> 00:19:46.218
Come to think of it,

00:19:46.218 --> 00:19:49.121
you've been on Starry Islet
for sixteen years now.

00:19:49.121 --> 00:19:51.557
- Just about.
- Just about, huh?

00:19:51.557 --> 00:19:55.928
By now, even Yang Guo and Little Dragon Maiden
would have reunited.

00:19:55.928 --> 00:19:57.829
That's an old story.

00:19:57.829 --> 00:20:00.565
Haven't you ever thought about
going back to the main island?

00:20:03.569 --> 00:20:05.337
I got what I deserved.

00:20:05.337 --> 00:20:07.072
It's better if I don't go back.

00:20:07.072 --> 00:20:08.340
Yes.

00:20:08.340 --> 00:20:10.075
You are guilty.

00:20:10.075 --> 00:20:11.076
Your only crime is not being drunk enough!

00:20:11.076 --> 00:20:12.444
-

00:20:12.444 --> 00:20:13.444
That's right!

00:20:13.444 --> 00:20:15.749
You're not allowed to go anywhere
until you're drunk.

00:20:15.749 --> 00:20:16.781
Hey, do you guys remember?

00:20:16.781 --> 00:20:18.617
Every time he buys a ferry ticket,

00:20:18.617 --> 00:20:21.820
some disaster is guaranteed to happen.

00:20:21.820 --> 00:20:24.022
You and the main island are just...

00:20:24.022 --> 00:20:27.259
Incompatible! You clash!

00:20:27.259 --> 00:20:28.866
Bottoms up!

00:20:31.597 --> 00:20:34.666
- What's wrong?
- I can't drink anymore.

00:20:34.666 --> 00:20:36.535
I'm just kidding.

00:20:36.535 --> 00:20:38.569
There's more food here.

00:20:42.474 --> 00:20:45.510
Xiao You, come eat with us.

00:20:45.510 --> 00:20:46.645
No, thanks.

00:20:46.645 --> 00:20:48.680
I don't have much of an appetite.

00:20:48.680 --> 00:20:51.216
Then have a drink.

00:20:51.216 --> 00:20:53.619
Come on, drink with us!

00:20:53.619 --> 00:20:54.753
Help yourself.

00:20:54.753 --> 00:20:57.522
Drink up.

00:20:59.691 --> 00:21:02.261
Mr. Hua, happy birthday.

00:21:02.261 --> 00:21:03.562
Thank you.

00:21:03.562 --> 00:21:05.797
I also wish you all the best
and that all your dreams come true.

00:21:05.797 --> 00:21:07.443
Thank you, Mr. Hua.

00:21:10.869 --> 00:21:12.004
What's wrong? Are you not feeling well?

00:21:12.004 --> 00:21:12.970
Let me take a look at you.

00:21:12.970 --> 00:21:14.473
I'll be fine after I go back
and sleep for a bit.

00:21:14.473 --> 00:21:16.041
Let him check you here.
There's no consultation fee.

00:21:16.041 --> 00:21:16.741
Yeah!

00:21:16.741 --> 00:21:18.644
Your problem is you haven't drank enough.

00:21:18.644 --> 00:21:19.711
Come on, let's toast the village chief.

00:21:19.711 --> 00:21:20.711
The village chief will drink with you.

00:21:20.711 --> 00:21:22.180
Come on.

00:21:24.650 --> 00:21:25.784
Drink more.

00:21:25.784 --> 00:21:27.418
That's right.

00:21:29.855 --> 00:21:31.657
Mr. Hua, about yesterday...

00:21:31.657 --> 00:21:32.689
It's nothing.

00:21:32.689 --> 00:21:34.393
We'll talk about yesterday later.

00:21:34.393 --> 00:21:35.860
It's fine.

00:21:36.695 --> 00:21:38.597
Come on, let's drink together.

00:21:38.597 --> 00:21:40.932
Aren't you going to drink with Angela?

00:21:42.434 --> 00:21:44.469
A toast to Angela!

00:21:44.469 --> 00:21:46.270
You drink half.

00:21:50.175 --> 00:21:52.941
That's enough, Li Wan Zhe. Stop drinking.

00:21:55.914 --> 00:21:57.182
Chief Wang, watch me perform.

00:21:57.182 --> 00:22:00.152
Thank you for always taking care of me.

00:22:00.152 --> 00:22:02.487
Come on. Chief Wang, let's drink.

00:22:02.487 --> 00:22:03.522
You're really thirsty, aren't you?

00:22:03.522 --> 00:22:04.656
Wait for me. I need to go pee.

00:22:04.656 --> 00:22:05.724
- I'm going to go pee first.
- Chief Wang!

00:22:05.724 --> 00:22:08.226
- You drink first.
- Where are you going, Chief Wang?

00:22:08.226 --> 00:22:09.895
Are you using the bathroom
as an excuse to run away?

00:22:09.895 --> 00:22:10.929
- You do this every time.
- I'm done grilling over there.

00:22:10.929 --> 00:22:11.929
-

00:22:11.929 --> 00:22:14.165
I'm here to drink with everyone.

00:22:19.404 --> 00:22:21.084
I'll drink with you.

00:22:23.241 --> 00:22:25.001
Li Wan Zhe!

00:22:26.078 --> 00:22:27.446
Where's Li Wan Zhe?

00:22:27.446 --> 00:22:29.847
Li Wan Zhe is dancing over there.

00:22:34.953 --> 00:22:37.155
The carp jumping over the dragon gate!

00:22:37.155 --> 00:22:38.422
Come on.

00:22:46.665 --> 00:22:48.900
I can't help it that I gave birth
to someone like Li Wan Zhe.

00:22:48.900 --> 00:22:50.836
- Did I really give birth to him?
- Of course you did.

00:22:50.836 --> 00:22:52.537
- He's a good kid.
- Sometimes I'm not so sure.

00:22:52.537 --> 00:22:53.939
I'm just not sure.

00:22:53.939 --> 00:22:55.874
It's hard to be sure.

00:22:55.874 --> 00:22:57.842
I'll drink with you.

00:23:10.589 --> 00:23:12.423
I'm sorry.

00:23:14.593 --> 00:23:16.794
It's all my fault.

00:23:18.096 --> 00:23:20.165
- Hua.
- Please forgive me.

00:23:20.165 --> 00:23:21.500
He's been like this for a while.

00:23:21.500 --> 00:23:22.768
Do you have any medicine for him?

00:23:22.768 --> 00:23:24.070
- Help him out.
- Don't ignore me.

00:23:24.070 --> 00:23:26.972
I have the medicine.
Give him three more bottles.

00:23:26.972 --> 00:23:28.106
That'll shut him up.

00:23:28.106 --> 00:23:29.608
Drink up.

00:23:29.608 --> 00:23:32.076
Come on, drink.

00:23:32.911 --> 00:23:35.114
He's been mistaking me
for someone else all day.

00:23:35.114 --> 00:23:36.982
- Dad.
- Mr. He, I'm sorry.

00:23:36.982 --> 00:23:38.283
Xiao You, you're drunk.

00:23:38.283 --> 00:23:40.051
- Xiao You.
- Don't touch me.

00:23:40.051 --> 00:23:41.186
At least my Li Wan Zhe

00:23:41.186 --> 00:23:42.788
doesn't go around calling random people "Dad."

00:23:42.788 --> 00:23:43.822
You won't drink with me?

00:23:43.822 --> 00:23:46.670
- Go to sleep.
- I'm not drinking with you.

00:23:50.028 --> 00:23:52.264
You want to drink with me?

00:23:52.264 --> 00:23:54.498
Fine, I'll drink with you.

00:24:00.205 --> 00:24:01.373
Xiao You.

00:24:01.373 --> 00:24:02.407
Let's go.

00:24:02.407 --> 00:24:04.142
Xiao You.

00:24:04.142 --> 00:24:06.712
That wine is quite expensive.

00:24:06.712 --> 00:24:07.712
I'll take care of him.

00:24:07.712 --> 00:24:08.713
- Take more.
- Xiao You.

00:24:08.713 --> 00:24:10.416
Take a few more.

00:24:13.986 --> 00:24:14.986
Xiao You.

00:24:14.986 --> 00:24:16.188
Has he lost his mind?

00:24:16.188 --> 00:24:18.072
Xiao You, slow down.

00:24:26.965 --> 00:24:28.978
Where are you trying to go?

00:24:42.514 --> 00:24:43.849
That's enough. Stop drinking.

00:24:43.849 --> 00:24:46.384
- You've had too much.
- Don't mess with me.

00:24:50.021 --> 00:24:52.958
If you don't want to drink, then go home.

00:24:52.958 --> 00:24:55.132
Just leave me alone, okay?

00:24:57.028 --> 00:24:58.830
Enough.

00:24:58.830 --> 00:25:01.034
Let's go back to the inn.

00:25:01.034 --> 00:25:03.055
Go back to what inn?

00:25:04.336 --> 00:25:07.072
Let me tell you something.

00:25:07.072 --> 00:25:09.207
If I don't finish my drink today,

00:25:09.207 --> 00:25:11.676
I'm not going back.

00:25:11.676 --> 00:25:13.006
Understand?

00:25:16.915 --> 00:25:18.514
You're drunk.

00:25:19.484 --> 00:25:21.009
What are you doing?

00:25:23.722 --> 00:25:25.449
I'm telling you,

00:25:26.358 --> 00:25:30.280
I won't go back until I finish my drink.

00:25:31.129 --> 00:25:33.798
What are you doing? Stop drinking.

00:25:34.466 --> 00:25:35.534
Xiao You.

00:25:35.534 --> 00:25:36.801
Okay, that's enough.

00:25:36.801 --> 00:25:38.937
Don't take my drink!

00:25:38.937 --> 00:25:41.172
You've had too much.

00:25:48.613 --> 00:25:50.314
Fine, how about this?

00:25:53.652 --> 00:25:55.020
I'll chug this bottle,

00:25:55.020 --> 00:25:57.121
then we'll go back to the inn, okay?

00:25:59.257 --> 00:26:01.021
You promise?

00:26:15.407 --> 00:26:16.908
Have they lost their minds?

00:26:16.908 --> 00:26:19.210
They've gone totally nuts.

00:26:19.945 --> 00:26:21.212
Pick up your glass. Hurry up.

00:26:21.212 --> 00:26:22.981
Go toast Mr. Hua.

00:26:22.981 --> 00:26:24.482
- Hurry up.
- It must be hereditary.

00:26:24.482 --> 00:26:25.483
Hurry up.

00:26:25.483 --> 00:26:28.520
- Hereditary? From whom?
- Medically speaking, it's genetic.

00:26:28.520 --> 00:26:30.755
Mr. Hua, happy birthday to you.

00:26:30.755 --> 00:26:32.624
- Thank you, everyone.
- Happy birthday!

00:26:32.624 --> 00:26:36.027
And Mr. He, thank you.

00:26:36.027 --> 00:26:37.896
Thank you, "Home is He-re".

00:26:37.896 --> 00:26:39.531
I really love this place.

00:26:39.531 --> 00:26:43.001
Cheers!

00:26:43.001 --> 00:26:45.070
I really don't want to let it go.

00:26:45.070 --> 00:26:46.271
Okay, you've had too much.

00:26:46.271 --> 00:26:47.872
Let's go watch the dancing, okay?

00:26:47.872 --> 00:26:49.809
Come on, let's dance.

00:26:49.809 --> 00:26:50.809
Let's go.

00:26:50.809 --> 00:26:52.277
Come on, let's dance.

00:26:52.277 --> 00:26:54.045
Let's go dance.

00:26:54.045 --> 00:26:55.947
I really love this place.

00:26:55.947 --> 00:26:58.350
It's the girls' turn to dance.

00:26:58.350 --> 00:27:00.251
The girls are up!

00:27:00.952 --> 00:27:02.953
What did he mean by that?

00:27:05.523 --> 00:27:08.193
I sold the inn.

00:27:08.193 --> 00:27:09.994
You sold it?

00:27:10.695 --> 00:27:12.364
Okay, come on.

00:27:12.364 --> 00:27:13.498
It's my birthday today.
Let's not talk about this.

00:27:13.498 --> 00:27:14.499
-

00:27:14.499 --> 00:27:16.701
It has nothing to do with that.

00:27:16.701 --> 00:27:18.070
- But he...
- It does.

00:27:18.070 --> 00:27:19.070
What about him?

00:27:19.070 --> 00:27:21.106
- Hey!
- A, B, C, D, okay?

00:27:21.106 --> 00:27:23.079
You're so annoying.

00:27:30.782 --> 00:27:32.317
I'm done drinking.

00:27:32.317 --> 00:27:35.119
Let's go home.

00:27:40.959 --> 00:27:43.060
That's the wrong way.

00:27:58.576 --> 00:28:01.146
Can you tell me now?

00:28:01.146 --> 00:28:03.280
What exactly are you sad about?

00:28:04.115 --> 00:28:06.685
Am I sad?

00:28:06.685 --> 00:28:09.920
I'm super happy!

00:28:09.920 --> 00:28:13.024
I've had more to drink today
than ever before in my life.

00:28:13.024 --> 00:28:15.758
Tell me the truth.

00:28:15.758 --> 00:28:18.098
I'm super happy about everything.

00:28:18.098 --> 00:28:21.397
Don't pull me.

00:28:21.397 --> 00:28:23.472
I can walk by myself.

00:28:29.207 --> 00:28:30.375
Chen Hao Wei.

00:28:30.375 --> 00:28:31.710
Don't ever come looking for me again.

00:28:31.710 --> 00:28:32.845
What do you mean?

00:28:32.845 --> 00:28:35.546
He Xiang Yong.

00:28:42.120 --> 00:28:44.095
You just turned and walked away.

00:28:47.258 --> 00:28:49.827
You just turned and walked away like that.

00:28:53.398 --> 00:28:55.699
I finally found you.

00:28:56.468 --> 00:28:58.959
I won't let go ever again.

00:29:00.105 --> 00:29:01.721
He Xiang Yong.

00:29:38.977 --> 00:29:40.845
Page 18 isn't on the exam.
[Epilogue]

00:29:40.845 --> 00:29:44.117
Happy birthday to you.

00:29:45.984 --> 00:29:48.219
This is the first time
I've given someone a painting.

00:29:48.219 --> 00:29:49.654
I hope you like it.

00:29:49.654 --> 00:29:51.856
Like it?

00:29:51.856 --> 00:29:53.992
This is the best birthday gift
I've ever received.

00:29:53.992 --> 00:29:56.294
How could I not like it?

00:29:56.294 --> 00:30:00.098
I like it very, very, very much.

00:30:00.098 --> 00:30:01.865
That's good.

00:30:06.571 --> 00:30:08.039
How could you forget the most important part?

00:30:08.039 --> 00:30:10.775
The signature. Hurry and sign it.

00:30:10.775 --> 00:30:11.810
When you become famous one day,

00:30:11.810 --> 00:30:14.312
I'm going to brag to everyone
that I was your very first fan.

00:30:14.312 --> 00:30:16.648
You're so dramatic.

00:30:16.648 --> 00:30:18.383
He Xiang Yong.

00:30:18.383 --> 00:30:21.885
One day, you'll definitely become
a world-famous painter.

00:30:23.221 --> 00:30:25.623
You're so excited
about this year's birthday gift.

00:30:25.623 --> 00:30:27.892
What am I going to do next year?

00:30:27.892 --> 00:30:30.428
How about for my birthday next year,

00:30:30.428 --> 00:30:31.596
you take me back to your home
to see real sea turtles?

00:30:31.596 --> 00:30:32.730
-

00:30:32.730 --> 00:30:35.099
Sure. It's a deal.

00:30:36.067 --> 00:30:41.973
Back then, neither of us knew that those words

00:30:41.973 --> 00:30:44.441
would never have the chance to come true.

00:31:09.567 --> 00:31:12.270
So, did you kiss Chen Hao Wei last night?

00:31:12.270 --> 00:31:13.671
"I'm so happy."

00:31:13.671 --> 00:31:16.140
That's what you said while hugging me.

00:31:16.140 --> 00:31:17.909
My wish came true so easily.

00:31:17.909 --> 00:31:21.646
Don't you think it feels a bit surreal?

00:31:21.646 --> 00:31:23.448
I think He Xiang Yong

00:31:23.448 --> 00:31:26.180
shouldn't use Xiao You as a substitute.